text: In this experiement there will be 4 blocks. Press "Next" to enter the block.

In this task, you will hear a sequence of syllables with different pitches, a pause, then another sequence with different pitches. Your task is to determine whether the PITCHes in the first sequence are in the same or different order than the PITCHes in the second sequence. After hearing these two sequences, you will be prompted to indicate whether these sequences are the "same" or "different". Press "Next" to start trials.
